# C-Basics

This repository contains basic C programming programs for beginners.
Programs are organized day-wise to build strong fundamentals.

## Day 1 – Basics
- Hello World
- Input and Output
- Sum of two numbers

## Day 2 – Conditional Statements
- Even or Odd
- Positive or Negative
- Largest of Two Numbers

## How to Run
1. Install GCC compiler
2. Go to the required day folder
3. Compile and run:
   gcc filename.c
   ./a.out

## Language Used
- C
